37 Chapter 3. Continuing Age Verification
38 Sec. 1. (a) Not later than fourteen (14) days after the first date
39 on which an Indiana account holder has spent at least twenty-five
40 (25) hours in a single six (6) month period using a covered social
41 media provider's social media platform, the covered social media
42 provider shall:
43 (1) make reasonable efforts; and
44 (2) use reasonable means, taking into consideration the
